#: {{zh-x|甲：「姐姐{jie}，看 好 了，這{zhèi} 魚 四 斤 高-高{gāor} 的。」乙：「嘛{mà} 高-高{gāor} 的！再 給 饒 一 條。」|A: “Look, ma'am, all this fish is heavier than two kilos already! {{q|pointing to the steelyard balance which is tilted towards the fish side}}”<br>B: “What are you talking about! '''Add''' another fish please (so that it is actually ‘two kilos' worth of fish’).”|M-TJ}}
